QuestData.Title: Aogexon's Fang
QuestData.CompletionText: Aogexon is one of the most feared beasts in Nagrand, and one of the largest and most dangerous forest stalkers ever seen!$b$bI've already been approached by a number of a collectors interested in obtaining one of Aogexon's deadly fangs. If you are up for the challenge, Aogexon can sometimes be found lurking in the swamp not far from here.$b$bGood luck!
